#Eng texts by Amaroth
0:Amaroth
1:You pacified the bandits, but there was little satisfaction in doing so. The bandits turned out to be just poor refugees pushed into their acts by unknown raiders invading the [$14FF14]Duke Royce[]'s lands. Since Royce was a friend to your father, you promised help to the leader of the bandits, [$61793F]Graham[]. It is time to get to the bottom of what is going on in Royce's duchy.

